modName: Skyfalls and SkyMills esp solitude skymill lod fix
summary:
it's a small but effective distant lod fix for the (earlier) disappearing solitude skymill tower viewing from far distance.while the animated rotor is still visible.
the patched esp solves this porblem. just replace the original esp (V3.3.2) with the patched one. nothing else is changed.
descriptionHtml:
it's a small but effective distant lod fix for the (earlier) disappearing solitude skymill tower viewing from far distance.while the animated rotor is still visible and rotating free in the air.
the patched esp solves this minor but annyoing glich (if encountered). just replace the original esp (V3.3.2) with the patched one. nothing else is changed.
